{"tid":546269,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[Apple rip]美國計劃要求所有手機需以可拆卸電池設計！","createTime":"2018-01-31T11:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T15:40:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5357b8820c31d4cea0f2e25f2fbd908e81a110c0","tid":546269,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"據外媒報道，近日美國華盛頓州率先計劃為電子產品的可維修性立法，要求手機的電池為可拆卸方便維修，防止電子污染，並且美國政府計劃將這個模式推廣至全國。美國立法會認為：「手機電池用膠水黏在主板上，人為增加了拆修和維修的難度，不符合環保和重復利用的原則，所以電池必須是可拆卸可更換的。」<br />\n<br />\n如果這個政策正式實施，那麼以後根據美國立法的規定，手機電池必須是可拆卸性的，這也意味著將來的 iPhone 也要強行執行這一規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/01/30/usa-phone-battery-removable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2Fusa-phone-battery-removable%2F&d=h76QI0Eho2BebNq1QwTO2uargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a2331c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/01/30/usa-phone-battery-removable/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef979ef0cb824f65cc5cb21158666dbbf4154b4","tid":546269,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d55ca8c14a3e0fbd61b5e93cc4dd19dbdff6c97","tid":546269,"uid":142405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88eac98ba366a619cc9f5339d3bdadff574f22a","tid